==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wharfage
<hw>Wharf"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The fee or duty paid for the privilege of using a
wharf for loading or unloading goods; pierage, collectively;
quayage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A wharf or wharfs, collectively; wharfing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wharfing</ent>⟦br⟧
